		</p>
	  </div> <!-- .well -->
    </div>
	<div class="row"> 
	  <div class="well sidebar">
		<h3>Software Development</h3>
<%= t "about.developers", default: "The software development team at Peoplenetz has years of experience working on enterprise level applications. They have specialzed in building software that manages vast amounts of data. Our development team not only has expertise Java, Flex, Flash and Ruby on Rails but also has the statistical expertise to provide organiations with unparalleled analytic capabilities without complication." %>
	  </div> <!-- .well -->
	</div>
  </div> <!-- /span -->
